data.description: SELLER FINANCING AVAILABLE with much lower than market interest rates.  Buyer can get a rate in the mid 5’s to mid 7’s depending on down payment, MINIMUM of 10% down and buyer must get pre-approved with www.LeahyLending.com for seller financing transaction. NO formal underwriting, lower closing costs, no discount points. With the seller financing you can buy this $527,500 home for the same payment as a $406,207 home.      Welcome to this exceptional former model home! From the moment you step inside, you'll feel the warmth and charm that sets this residence apart from the rest. No detail has been spared, gorgeous hardwood floors, elegant tile, and upgraded flooring throughout.  This home is not only beautiful but also smartly designed with features like a wired surround sound system and security camera setup. The exterior boasts lush landscaping and a Holiday Light Package, making your home the envy of the neighborhood during the festive season.  The second level offers a versatile Bonus Room and a Full Bath, along with Two Flex Spaces that can be adapted to your specific needs. Whether you work from home, desire a formal dining room, homeschool your children, or need a dedicated crafting area, this home accommodates your lifestyle effortlessly.  Embrace outdoor living to the fullest. This outdoor space is just right for entertainment. Whether you're hosting gatherings with friends and family or simply relishing the serenity of the season, this backyard is an ideal setting. The location is unbeatable, with a short drive to the Dell Diamond, Kalahari resorts, Round Rock Premium Outlets, Teravista Golf Course, Texas State University-Round Rock, and the new Samsung Semiconductor site.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this extraordinary home your own. It's everything you've been searching for in a residence – stylish, practical, and perfectly located for all your needs.
